div.div:
User Stories:
1. As a customer, so that I can communicate my wishes to the store, I would like to place a detailed order on my desired products.
2. As the owner, so that I can be transparent to my customers, I would like to be able to update the price and quantity of a product.
3. As the owner, so that I can keep track of my orders, I would like to have a list of all orders currently being processed.
4. As the owner, so that I can look back on old orders, I would like keep track of all the completed orders.
